        "name": "Life Drain",
        "text": "*Melee Weapon Attack:* atk[str] to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. *Hit:* dmg[1d6 + str] necrotic damage. The target must succeed on a DC 13 Constitution saving throw or its hit point maximum is reduced by an amount equal to the damage taken. This reduction lasts until the target finishes a long rest. The target dies if this effect reduces its hit point maximum to 0.\n  A humanoid slain by this attack rises 24 hours later as a zombie under [name]'s control, unless the humanoid is restored to life or its body is destroyed. [name] can have no more than twelve zombies under its control at one time."
      },
      {
        "name": "Longsword",
        "text": "*Melee Weapon Attack:* atk[str] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* dmg[1d8 + str] slashing damage, or dmg[1d10 + str] slashing damage if used with two hands."
